harmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[4] "Product Information. Cozaar (losartan)." Merck & Co, Inc, West Point, PA.[5] "Product Information. Prepopik (citric acid/Mg oxide/Na picosulfate)." Ferring Pharmaceuticals Inc, Tarrytown, NY.[6] "Product Information. Golytely (polyethylene glycol electrolyte solution)." Braintree, Braintree, MA.', 'Tamsulosin, Tinidazole, Ascorbic acid, Metronidazole, Simeprevir, Rosuvastatin, Sulfadiazine, Lactic acid, Mitapivat, Amphotericin B, Clindamycin, More', 'Alvimopan, Sorbitol, Magnesium sulfate, Methylnaltrexone, Tegaserod, Magnesium oxide, Naloxegol, Plecanatide, Lubiprostone, Methylcellulose, Mannitol, More', 1767369485);
